            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-0 text-white">Our Mission</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-0" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Equip building professionals with practical skills, local project experience, and career-ready software training.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="info-strip-card">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <i class="bi bi-eye" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--warm-light);"></i>
            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-0 text-white">Our Vision</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-0" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">A stronger construction sector across Rwanda through modern education, industry partnerships, and digital design excellence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="info-strip-card">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--warm-light);"></i>
            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-0 text-white">Our Promise</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-0" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Clear, practical training paths with internship support and real-world project outcomes.</p>
